---
import StudioWorkflowLayout from "../layouts/StudioWorkflowLayout.astro";
---

<StudioWorkflowLayout
  title="Studio v2 总览 | Atlas AI Tools"
  description="全景总览页：看热点、草稿、审核和发布进度，再进入对应步骤页处理细节。"
  currentStep="overview"
>
  <section class="workflow-panel">
    <div class="workflow-page-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-kicker">Overview</div>
        <h2>先看全景，再决定先做哪一步</h2>
        <p>
          这里不是所有内容的堆叠长页，而是工作流总控台。你先确认当前卡在哪一步，再进入单独步骤页处理。
        </p>
      </div>
      <a class="workflow-link-button" href="/studio/workspace">打开旧版工作台</a>
    </div>
    <div class="workflow-step-grid" id="workflow-overview-step-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="workflow-panel">
    <div class="workflow-page-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-kicker">Recent publish activity</div>
        <h2>最近发布记录</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="workflow-list" id="workflow-overview-publish-log"></div>
  </section>

  <script type="module">
    import { initStudioWorkflowPage } from "../lib/studio-workflow-client";

    void initStudioWorkflowPage("overview");
  </script>
</StudioWorkflowLayout>
